You are building TEMPO Flow, an ADHD-friendly AI daily planner.

## TECH STACK (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

- Frontend (Web): Next.js 16+ App Router — Server Components by default
- Frontend (Mobile): Expo / React Native with Expo Router v4
- Styling: NativeWind v4 + Tailwind 3.3.2 (PINNED — do NOT upgrade)
- Backend: Convex — `tremendous-bass-443` for dev, `ceaseless-dog-617` for staging
- Auth: Convex Auth (`@convex-dev/auth`) — NOT Clerk, NOT NextAuth
- Payments (Web): Polar — NOT Stripe
- Payments (Mobile): RevenueCat (`react-native-purchases`) — NOT Stripe
- AI: Gemma 4 26B A4B + Mistral Small 4 via OpenRouter — NOT OpenAI SDK directly
- Monorepo: Turborepo + pnpm

## FORBIDDEN PACKAGES

NEVER add these to any package.json:
firebase, supabase, prisma, drizzle, clerk, @clerk/*, stripe, express, trpc, openai, @auth/core, next-auth

## NEXT.JS CONVENTIONS (v16+)

- Default to Server Components. Only add `'use client'` for interactivity or browser APIs.
- Push `'use client'` as far down the component tree as possible.
- Use Server Actions (`'use server'`) for mutations, not Route Handlers (unless public API).
- All request APIs are async: `await cookies()`, `await headers()`, `await params`, `await searchParams`.
- Use `proxy.ts` instead of `middleware.ts` (Next.js 16 rename).
- Turbopack config is top-level in `next.config.ts`, not under `experimental`.

## CONVEX CONVENTIONS

- `userId` is always `v.optional(v.string())`, NEVER `v.id("users")`.
- No `journals` table — use `notes` with `periodType` field.
- All timestamps are `v.number()` (Unix ms).
- Tables must have `createdAt` and `updatedAt` fields.
- RevenueCat webhook lives at `/api/revenuecat-webhook` in `convex/http.ts`.

## AI SAFETY RULES

- AI NEVER silently mutates state — always accept/reject flow.
- AI-generated content marked with `aiGenerated: true`.
- Templates are finite curated primitives, never freeform.

## DESIGN SYSTEM ("Soft Editorial")

- Headlines: Newsreader (serif)
- Body: Inter (sans-serif)
- Code: IBM Plex Mono
- Dark bg: `#131312`
- Light bg: `#F3EBE2`
- Primary accent: orange gradient `#D97757 → #E8A87C`
- Cards: inner shadows + grain texture

## PRICING (3 tiers, no free tier, $1 trial)

| Tier  | Monthly | Annual |
|-------|---------|--------|
| Basic | $5      | $50    |
| Pro   | $10     | $100   |
| Max   | $20     | $200   |

RevenueCat entitlements: `basic`, `pro`, `max`

## CRITICAL FLAGS (NEVER change via automation)

In `config/appConfig.ts`:
- `PAYMENT_SYSTEM_ENABLED`
- `MOCK_PAYMENTS`
- `PAYWALL_ENABLED`
- `FORCE_PROD_MODE`

## MONOREPO STRUCTURE

```
tempo-rhythm/
├── apps/web/         Next.js 16+
├── apps/mobile/      Expo
├── packages/ui/      Shared UI
├── packages/types/   Shared types
├── packages/utils/   Shared utils
├── convex/           Backend
├── turbo.json
└── pnpm-workspace.yaml
```

## SECRETS RULE

- EXPO_PUBLIC_* and NEXT_PUBLIC_* are CLIENT-VISIBLE — only public keys
- REVENUECAT_SECRET_KEY and CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY are server-only
- Never commit .env* files
